won't listen to us

07:42.896 --> 07:45.464
Because he, or she,
has been hanging out

07:45.466 --> 07:46.832
With a really bad dude.

07:46.834 --> 07:47.532
- Oh, I see.

07:47.534 --> 07:50.101
Your friend's having
a gender identity crisis.

07:50.103 --> 07:52.604
- No, our friend
is skipping school

07:52.606 --> 07:56.908
And turning into
a gange-head.

07:56.910 --> 07:59.544
- You strike me as being
very concerned

07:59.546 --> 08:00.812
About your friend.

08:00.814 --> 08:03.448
I'd go so far as
to call you

08:03.450 --> 08:06.618
The concerned friends.

08:06.620 --> 08:08.954
My advice is to get involved

08:08.956 --> 08:11.223
In an after-school activity.

08:11.225 --> 08:13.959
Ming, can you remove
your hat please?

08:19.899 --> 08:21.633
Have you ever thought
about acting?

08:21.635 --> 08:24.369
Tamara had a memorable
scenery-chewing turn

08:24.371 --> 08:26.938
In <i>dead stacey,</i>
but what about you two?

08:26.940 --> 08:27.906
- I was in it too.

08:27.908 --> 08:29.274
- Eh, not so memorable.

08:29.276 --> 08:30.242
- How is acting
going to help?

08:30.244 --> 08:32.277
- It'll free you up
as people.

08:32.279 --> 08:33.245
Okay, please stand up.

08:33.246 --> 08:36.982
I'd like to try
some improv.

08:36.984 --> 08:37.649
- I'm confused.

08:37.650 --> 08:39.116
- Yeah, what are we supposed
to be doing?

08:39.119 --> 08:40.684
- You're supposed
to be confused,

08:40.687 --> 08:42.053
And you are succeeding.

08:42.054 --> 08:44.389
You, you're about to be shipped
off to a german work camp.

08:44.391 --> 08:46.925
You can only bring one friend.
The other friend will die.

08:46.927 --> 08:48.260
Who do you choose?
Don't think!

08:48.262 --> 08:49.261
- I don't know,
I can't decide!

08:49.263 --> 08:51.663
But I would rather die than
kill off one of my friends.

08:51.665 --> 08:54.299
- Oh, impressive.

08:55.067 --> 08:59.738
You two in the back,
please step forward.

08:59.740 --> 09:02.641
Jake, take one step back.

09:04.110 --> 09:06.745
You two in the front row,
congratulations, you made it.

09:06.747 --> 09:09.614
- [squeals]
- you in the back,

09:09.616 --> 09:10.181
I'm sorry.

09:10.183 --> 09:12.517
You'll have to tell your mom
that you'll be late to dinner,

09:12.519 --> 09:14.119
Because you made it too!
- I made what?

09:14.121 --> 09:16.288
- My a.S.S.,
my after school special video.

09:16.290 --> 09:18.423
- No, I'm not doing that.
- Not my jam.

09:18.425 --> 09:20.659
- I'll give you a mental health
day pass to skip school.

09:20.661 --> 09:21.693
- Done.
- I'm in.

09:21.695 --> 09:23.295
- I don't need the pass.

09:26.632 --> 09:29.901
- Have you started
your essay yet?

09:29.903 --> 09:32.003
- I'll write it tonight.

09:32.005 --> 09:32.671
If I can stay awake.

09:32.673 --> 09:35.373
What time did you leave
last night--2:00?

09:35.375 --> 09:40.111
- Mm, more like 3:00.

09:40.113 --> 09:42.581
Hey.

09:42.583 --> 09:44.816
- What is it?

09:44.818 --> 09:48.520
- A ticket for the "a" train.

09:49.622 --> 09:53.491
- What if I need
a round-trip ticket?

09:55.161 --> 09:58.063
[energetic techno music]

09:58.065 --> 09:59.965
I hadn't decided what to write
my essay about,

09:59.967 --> 10:02.367
So I was just writing anything
that popped into my head.

10:02.369 --> 10:04.469
But why was it so hard to settle
on a subject matter?

10:04.471 --> 10:06.271
Hero or villain?
Maybe running around the block

10:06.273 --> 10:07.339
A few times
would help me decide.

10:07.341 --> 10:09.941
I had never felt so inspired
and yet so scattered.

10:09.943 --> 10:13.044
It was weird and awesome,
but what was even awesomer--

10:13.046 --> 10:14.512
[soft piano music]
- there were certain things

10:14.514 --> 10:16.481
I had learned about myself
over the years,

10:16.483 --> 10:18.683
But the single
most important thing was

10:18.685 --> 10:23.822
I loved writing about me
and all my stupid problems.

10:23.824 --> 10:25.490
Maybe my side braid
was cutting off

10:25.492 --> 10:26.691
The circulation
to my brain,

10:26.693 --> 10:28.693
But I couldn't stop
doing dumb stuff

10:28.695 --> 10:29.794
I would regret later.

10:29.796 --> 10:31.129
- Cut!
[bell rings]

10:31.131 --> 10:33.331
Enough with the blogging.
Jesus.

10:33.333 --> 10:35.533
So boring.
Am I right?

10:35.535 --> 10:37.002
