- Watch yourself.

10:37.004 --> 10:40.405
I wrote you into the script,
and I can write you out.

10:40.407 --> 10:41.773
- This is about jenna.

10:41.775 --> 10:43.108
- And she is
not gonna like it.

10:43.110 --> 10:46.244
- Or it'll snap her
out of her insanity.

10:46.246 --> 10:46.678
- Okay.

10:46.680 --> 10:50.315
Let's move on to the
"establish the problem" montage.

10:50.317 --> 10:52.951
Kyle, you're
the good guy jock.

10:52.953 --> 10:54.319
Jake, you're the bad guy.

10:54.321 --> 10:55.654
- Why do I have to be
the bad guy?

10:55.656 --> 10:57.622
- 'cause you're always typecast
as a goody-goody.

10:57.624 --> 11:00.358
- In what?
- In life.

11:00.360 --> 11:01.559
[scoffs]

11:01.561 --> 11:03.828
- I wasn't always
a bad girl.

11:03.830 --> 11:05.463
I was just boring and lame.

11:05.465 --> 11:08.199
But lately, I had become
a hard-core bitch

11:08.201 --> 11:10.235
Who also happened to be
boring and lame.

11:10.237 --> 11:13.171
But in order to understand
how I got where I was,

11:13.173 --> 11:15.540
