where I'd been.

11:15.542 --> 11:18.009
After getting caught cheating
with calvin

11:18.011 --> 11:19.144
On my boyfriend, danny,

11:19.146 --> 11:20.779
I lost all my friends.

11:20.781 --> 11:21.713
I was alone.

11:21.715 --> 11:24.949
But it wasn't long
before I found a new friend

11:24.951 --> 11:26.785
To lift my spirits--

11:26.787 --> 11:28.019
Mary jane.

11:28.021 --> 11:30.388
I had become an addict
and a loser.

11:30.390 --> 11:31.523
Well...
[giggles]

11:31.525 --> 11:33.124
A more epic loser,

11:33.126 --> 11:36.428
Since I was a loser
from the start.

11:36.430 --> 11:37.862
But my piece de resistance
was pushing away

11:37.864 --> 11:40.231
The only people
who had to love me...

11:40.233 --> 11:41.232
[door clicks open]

11:41.234 --> 11:42.767
People who were far more
attractive than me

11:42.769 --> 11:44.869
And in no way, shape, or form
could have been

11:44.871 --> 11:46.037
My biological parents,

11:46.039 --> 11:47.305
Because they were
smokin' hot.

11:47.307 --> 11:49.674
I hate you and your boobs!
- I hate you!

11:49.676 --> 11:52.243
- And it made me want
to die...

11:52.245 --> 11:54.446
Even more than usual.

11:54.448 --> 11:56.748
[gags]

11:59.351 --> 12:00.652
- Hey, it's me.

12:00.654 --> 12:02.721
I'm just calling to say
I miss you.

12:02.723 --> 12:04.589
I know it's only been
ten seconds,

12:04.591 --> 12:06.024
But I miss you already.

12:06.026 --> 12:08.026
Meet me in my room
in 30?

12:08.028 --> 12:09.728
Okay, bye.
Whoa.

12:09.730 --> 12:11.296
- What the hell is this?

12:11.298 --> 12:13.765
- You're sick?
