12:13.767 --> 12:15.600
You don't even remember
your own lies.

12:15.602 --> 12:16.367
They're from valerie.

12:16.369 --> 12:18.570
- She's doing this lame video
project after school,

12:18.572 --> 12:19.871
And I can't waste
my time on that

12:19.873 --> 12:22.574
When I've got an important paper
to write for mr. Hart.

12:22.576 --> 12:25.110
It's gonna be published
in his lit magazine.

12:25.112 --> 12:26.277
Isn't that cool?

12:26.279 --> 12:27.812
- So you lied to valerie

12:27.814 --> 12:29.681
To get out of doing
her project,

12:29.683 --> 12:31.483
And you used me
as your excuse,

12:31.485 --> 12:32.617
Not to mention your dad,

12:32.619 --> 12:35.754
Who valerie now thinks
is some crazy sex fiend.

12:35.756 --> 12:38.823
Jenna, she sent me
a jellyfish balloon.

12:38.825 --> 12:41.092
- Mom, it's no big deal--
- eh!

12:41.094 --> 12:41.726
Get in the car.

12:41.728 --> 12:43.328
You are doing
this lame video,

12:43.330 --> 12:45.930
And on the way over,
you're gonna explain to me

12:45.932 --> 12:48.099
What a backwards
jellyfish is.

12:48.101 --> 12:49.000
- Cut!

12:49.002 --> 12:51.336
[bell rings]

12:51.338 --> 12:51.903
[sighs]

12:51.905 --> 12:54.239
I've seen rock bottom,
and that wasn't it.

12:54.241 --> 12:56.775
We are talking
depths of despair,

12:56.777 --> 13:00.145
Basement level,
absolute bottom.

13:00.147 --> 13:03.248
Like if your parents lost
all their money.

13:03.250 --> 13:07.418
- In that case, I would
definitely kill myself.

13:07.420 --> 13:08.586
If I were jenny.

13:08.588 --> 13:10.421
- I know how to make
fake blood.

13:10.423 --> 13:13.758
It totally looks real.
It even smells real.

13:13.760 --> 13:16.394
But it's not.

13:16.396 --> 13:17.162
[eerie screech]

13:17.164 --> 13:18.997
- No. No. No blood.
No dying.

13:18.999 --> 13:20.598
We are not gonna win
this contest

13:20.600 --> 13:21.232
With a sad ending.

13:21.234 --> 13:24.536
This isn't
the golden globes.

13:24.538 --> 13:28.439
- Jenny lives.

13:28.441 --> 13:29.073
- L-dog!

13:29.075 --> 13:31.976
So good to see you
back on your feet,

13:31.978 --> 13:33.244
You sneaky dickens, you.

13:33.246 --> 13:35.513
You know, I've always believed
in the power

13:35.515 --> 13:37.382
Of a good balloon arrangement.

13:37.384 --> 13:40.151
That's why they call it
"heal-ium".

13:40.153 --> 13:41.119
- And I am healed!

13:41.121 --> 13:45.857
Which means jenna doesn't have
to take care of me anymore.

13:45.859 --> 13:47.892
She is all yours.

13:47.894 --> 13:48.426
- Great!

13:48.428 --> 13:52.697
F.Y.I., it's a closed set.

13:52.699 --> 13:54.032
Pick up where we left off!
[bell rings]

13:54.034 --> 13:56.434
Annnd action!
Voiceover.

13:56.436 --> 13:57.902
- I had hit rock bottom,

13:57.904 --> 14:00.205
And it felt surprisingly
like home.

14:00.207 --> 14:02.173
Even though there was nowhere
to go but up,

14:02.175 --> 14:05.109
I wanted to stay there
and move in.

14:05.111 --> 14:06.344
- What is this?

14:06.346 --> 14:09.814
- An uber-tragic tale
about a loser girl

14:09.816 --> 14:12.150
Who wants to die,
called...

14:12.152 --> 14:16.087
<i>What are we gonna do</i>
<i>about jenny?</i>

14:17.523 --> 14:20.358
- You've got to be
[bleep] kidding me.

14:23.262 --> 14:25.363
- Jenna, you are going to be

14:25.365 --> 14:26.431
Concerned friend
number four.

14:26.433 --> 14:27.699
- Actually, I think I'd make

14:27.701 --> 14:28.833
A much better enemy.

14:28.835 --> 14:29.467
- No, no, no, no.

14:29.469 --> 14:31.302
You're way too goody-two-shoes
to pull that off.

14:31.304 --> 14:33.538
All right,
listen up, actors.

14:33.540 --> 14:34.606
You're in the mall.

14:34.608 --> 14:36.341
There are zombies
everywhere,

14:36.343 --> 14:38.443
And they're headed
for the food court--

14:38.445 --> 14:39.844
Only you are the food.

14:39.846 --> 14:43.648
That is your emotional state.
And action!

14:46.719 --> 14:47.518
- Get out of my room!

14:47.520 --> 14:50.288
- We can't watch you
throw away your life!

14:50.290 --> 14:51.456
- My life is over!

14:51.458 --> 14:52.957
I had a hot boyfriend
who loved me

14:52.959 --> 14:57.095
Even though I'm an unlovable,
plain loser freak

14:57.097 --> 14:57.962
With no fashion sense,

14:57.964 --> 15:01.032
But I dumped him
for a pothead douche hole,

15:01.034 --> 15:02.834
And now I have
to live with that,

15:02.836 --> 15:04.068
Which is why I get high

15:04.070 --> 15:05.470
Just to make it
through the day.

15:05.472 --> 15:07.772
- I don't care
if you hate us right now.

15:07.774 --> 15:10.408
We're your friends,
and you need to hear this.

15:10.410 --> 15:12.143
- I have no friends!

15:12.145 --> 15:13.077
I'm a loser!

15:13.079 --> 15:16.014
I'm so dirty and gross
and high,

15:16.016 --> 15:17.682
I just want to kill myself!

15:17.684 --> 15:19.517
- Stop talking like that.
We love you,

15:19.519 --> 15:20.551
And we're worried
about you.

15:20.553 --> 15:23.321
- Actually, jenny, I'm not
worried about you at all.

15:23.323 --> 15:24.689
You seem fine to me,

15:24.691 --> 15:26.324
So go on and live your life,

15:26.326 --> 15:27.892
Which is
none of our business.

15:27.894 --> 15:29.494
We'll leave you alone.

15:29.496 --> 15:30.495
- We already left her alone,

15:30.497 --> 15:32.864
And she made
some very bad choices.

15:32.866 --> 15:34.565
- So what?
They were her choices.

15:34.567 --> 15:35.900
- Were they?
Because it seemed like jenny

15:35.902 --> 15:39.070
Was just doing whatever
her boyfriend wanted her to do.

15:39.072 --> 15:41.339
- And that guy is bad news.

15:41.341 --> 15:43.374
- They're improvising.

15:43.376 --> 15:45.476
- Oh, improv.

15:45.478 --> 15:46.511
- You don't even know calvin,

15:46.513 --> 15:47.779
And I can say that
for a fact

15:47.781 --> 15:48.947
Because I hardly know him,

15:48.949 --> 15:50.248
Because we're too busy
getting high

15:50.250 --> 15:52.750
And doing it
to have an actual conversation.

15:52.752 --> 15:55.887
- Not true--you and calvin have
meaningful conversations

15:55.889 --> 15:56.587
All the time.

15:56.589 --> 15:57.655
- I think jenny's
just dating him

15:57.657 --> 15:59.190
'cause she likes hanging out
with a bad boy.

15:59.192 --> 16:02.327
- Or maybe because he has
the sweet pot connections.

16:02.329 --> 16:04.862
- Or maybe because he owns
a jet ski!

16:04.864 --> 16:06.965
- She's dating him
because she likes him.

16:06.967 --> 16:07.665
End of story.

16:07.667 --> 16:09.100
- All this fighting
and arguing

16:09.102 --> 16:11.069
Just makes me want
to die more!

16:11.071 --> 16:11.736
- You are so out of it,

16:11.738 --> 16:13.037
You don't even know
what you're saying!

16:13.039 --> 16:15.907
- I am not out of it,
and I don't need your help,

16:15.909 --> 16:17.108
So leave me alone.

16:17.110 --> 16:20.011
[the dig's <i>over you]</i>

16:20.013 --> 16:26.884
- ♪ fall into a dream

16:26.886 --> 16:30.388
♪ in a hollow room

16:30.390 --> 16:32.256
- Uh, give me a minute.

16:32.258 --> 16:34.592
- ♪ frozen in a sleep

16:34.594 --> 16:35.660
- Hey.

16:35.662 --> 16:36.394
- What?

16:36.396 --> 16:37.528
Are you gonna talk
to me too?

16:37.530 --> 16:39.430
Tell me I'm going
down the wrong path,

16:39.432 --> 16:41.232
Hanging out
with bad people?

16:41.234 --> 16:43.701
You wanna warn me?
Go for it.

16:43.703 --> 16:47.972
- ♪ calling out to me

16:47.974 --> 16:50.475
- Nope.

16:50.477 --> 16:54.445
- ♪ calling out my name

16:54.447 --> 16:55.813
- I'm sorry, j.

16:55.815 --> 16:59.684
You're suspended.

17:03.122 --> 17:05.857
- I got you the pills,
but this isn't enough.

17:05.858 --> 17:06.557
- It's all I got.

17:06.559 --> 17:08.259
I'll give you the rest
tomorrow, dude.

17:08.261 --> 17:08.826
I swear.

17:08.828 --> 17:10.461
- That's not good enough.

17:10.463 --> 17:13.297
Guys: [grunting]

17:13.299 --> 17:14.965
- Ugh!

17:14.968 --> 17:17.734
- Oh, my god,
you killed him!

17:17.737 --> 17:19.537
- Oh!

17:19.539 --> 17:21.239
[gasping]

17:21.241 --> 17:24.709
[dramatic synthesizer music]

17:24.711 --> 17:30.381
♪

17:30.383 --> 17:34.252
- Calvin!

17:34.254 --> 17:38.022
Nooo...

17:38.024 --> 17:39.690
All this fighting
and arguing

17:39.692 --> 17:42.393
Just makes me
want to die more!

17:42.395 --> 17:43.061
- You are so out of it,

17:43.063 --> 17:44.495
You don't even know
what you're saying.

17:44.497 --> 17:47.031
- I am not out of it,
and I don't need your help,

17:47.033 --> 17:47.799
So just leave me alone.

17:47.801 --> 17:50.301
- I just want
to kill myself!

17:50.303 --> 17:57.075
♪

17:57.077 --> 17:58.443
I wanted to die.

17:58.445 --> 17:59.110
I deserve to die.

17:59.112 --> 18:03.181
But I guess it's time for me
to start living...

18:03.183 --> 18:06.451
For now.

18:08.153 --> 18:11.456
[uplifting music]

18:11.458 --> 18:19.764
♪

18:22.835 --> 18:24.869
- First prize goes to...

18:24.871 --> 18:27.538
Valerie marks,
for her moving portrait

18:27.540 --> 18:31.943
Of a deeply troubled girl
who lost her way.

18:32.978 --> 18:36.981
Deeply troubled girl
who lost her way...

18:38.884 --> 18:40.618
- You are so out of it,
you don't even know

18:40.620 --> 18:41.352
What you're saying.

18:41.354 --> 18:43.387
- I am not out of it,
and I don't need your help,

18:43.389 --> 18:46.724
So just leave me alo--
[click]

18:46.726 --> 18:48.793
- Oh, my god.

18:48.795 --> 18:50.027
I was so busy
with my a.S.S.,

18:50.029 --> 18:53.131
I didn't see the a.S.S.
In front of my face.

18:53.133 --> 18:55.266
Jenna is jenny.

18:55.268 --> 18:57.135
[doorbell rings]

18:57.137 --> 18:59.137
[crickets chirping]

18:59.139 --> 18:59.837
- Why are you here?

18:59.839 --> 19:02.306
- I'm the help that arrives.
Yay!

19:02.308 --> 19:03.241
- Well, I don't need it,

19:03.243 --> 19:04.609
So why don't you be
the help

19:04.611 --> 19:05.443
That goes the hell away?

19:05.445 --> 19:06.477
- That's the pot talking.

19:06.479 --> 19:08.713
And I am sorry
that it took me so long

19:08.715 --> 19:11.582
To get up to speed--
which you might be on too.

19:11.584 --> 19:13.417
But I'm ready now.

19:13.419 --> 19:16.420
And as your friend,
I'm ready to help,

19:16.422 --> 19:18.222
'cause you're my girl.

19:18.224 --> 19:19.991
- Your girl.

19:19.993 --> 19:21.926
Don't you see
how weird that is?

19:21.928 --> 19:22.727
No, of course you don't,

19:22.729 --> 19:24.629
'cause you don't
understand boundaries.

19:24.631 --> 19:26.264
I'm not your friend,

19:26.266 --> 19:27.165
And I never have been.

19:27.167 --> 19:29.600
You're just
my guidance counselor,

19:29.602 --> 19:34.038
And a sucky one at that.

19:34.040 --> 19:34.805
Since I had known her,

19:34.807 --> 19:36.774
Valerie had always
crossed the line,

19:36.776 --> 19:38.609
And I had always
let it slide.

19:38.611 --> 19:41.212
But what was the point
of our special friendship

19:41.214 --> 19:42.914
If she wasn't going
to let me off

19:42.916 --> 19:44.515
With a slap on the wrist?

19:44.517 --> 19:45.383
As far as I was concerned,

19:45.385 --> 19:48.619
By suspending me,
she had crossed over the line

19:48.621 --> 19:51.722
To the point
of no return,

19:51.724 --> 19:55.359
Which is exactly
where I wanted to be...

19:58.564 --> 20:01.499
Until I found a drug
that was going to make me

20:01.501 --> 20:04.001
Feel <i>really</i> good--

20:04.003 --> 20:04.502
Revenge.

20:04.504 --> 20:06.170
The good thing
about having been suspended?

20:06.172 --> 20:09.507
I had plenty of time
to finish hart's assignment,

20:09.509 --> 20:11.776
And I knew exactly
who I would write about.

20:11.778 --> 20:15.846
Only there weren't going to be
any heroes in my story,

20:15.848 --> 20:17.648
Just a villain.

20:17.650 --> 20:19.584
One very familiar villain.

20:19.586 --> 20:24.088
- ♪ right to share
your queries ♪

20:24.090 --> 20:29.060
♪ of the day

20:29.062 --> 20:32.230
♪

20:32.232 --> 20:36.000
- It was time for me
to take that bitch down.

20:37.836 --> 20:39.136
- Next, on <i>awkward...</i>
What's going on here?

20:39.138 --> 20:40.871
- Lil' bitch,
this is your intervention.

20:40.873 --> 20:42.273
[grunts]
- you're all a bunch

20:42.275 --> 20:43.474
Of hypocrites.

20:43.476 --> 20:45.109
- You're grounded.
- I'm out.

20:45.111 --> 20:46.978
- If you leave...
- What?

20:46.980 --> 20:48.546
- Don't come back.

20:48.548 --> 20:50.781
- You made it.
[giggles]

20:50.783 --> 20:53.117
- You made it too.
[laughs nervously]

20:53.119 --> 20:55.052
So random, running
into angelique here.

20:55.054 --> 20:57.555
- Actually, I invited her.
